OL,4,CDisabled needs forgotten during Covid,
OL,5,CBBC research reveals
OL,6, Thousands of deaf and disabled people
OL,7, across the UK have told the BBC of the
OL,8, devastating impact the pandemic has had
OL,9, on their lives.
OL,11,FMost said their disability had worsened
OL,12,Fand more than 2,400 said routine, often
OL,13,Fvital, medical appointments had been
OL,14,Fcancelled.
OL,16,FMore than 3,300 people took part in the
OL,17,Fresearch carried out by the BBC.
OL,19,FDisability charity Scope said the
OL,20,Ffindings confirmed that disabled
OL,21,Fpeople's needs "had been forgotten".
